S.FORM: Forest Able nalecuhan i American, nanu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Forest Able i 1976 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 3 ku uwac atu silsil 20, namapili' tu nu Syracuse Nationals putiput putiput. 7 bulad 27 demiad, 1932 a mihca, Forest Able, miunduay.

Forest Able nalecohan i American, nano syobay kanas-mali miondoay no Amilika NBA nisakapot, pahanhanan to kawaw ayza. Forest Able i 1976 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 3 ko owac ato silsil 20, namapili' to no Syracose Nationals potipot potipot. 7 bolad 27 demiad, 1932 a mihca, Forest Able, miondoay.
